{"tid":940353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟明年係香港特區警察成立175周年定22周年？","createTime":"2018-12-14T01:01:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-14T02:04:58.000Z","uid":35790,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"c3e88c5984dc75ad2e1bc3ada12ef7ccbbb56cf1","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:01:28.000Z","msg":"隔牆有耳：警隊175歲<br />\n籲勿炒賣同樂日門票 - 李八方<br />\n<br />\n2018-12-14<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">明年5月1日就係香港警隊成立175周年，警隊已計劃連串慶祝活動</span>，頭炮就係明年1月12日、13日、19日及20日喺黃竹坑警察學院舉行嘅香港警隊175周年大匯演暨警民同樂日，除咗多個部隊表演同展示裝甲車等裝備外，亦加入科技元素，包括一齣講述警隊歷史嘅360度3D短片，參觀者要預先下載手機Apps「175AR」，就可以喺場內指定佈景板利用手機拍攝到飛虎隊或反恐特勤隊嘅VR影像。<br />\n<br />\n後日免費派1.2萬張飛<br />\n<br />\n警察學院副院長陳民德同八方講，同樂日為期四日，每日兩場，分別早上十點同下晝兩點，八場合共1.2萬張門票，市民可於後日早上八點半起到15個指定地點索取，每人免費限取兩張兼可以選擇時段，先到先得，平均每個地點會派發700至900張門票，警方呼籲市民千祈唔好炒賣，如果發現有不法活動會追查㗎。<br />\n&lt;蘋果&gt;"},{"pid":"de67e8851f7977a42fb9808cdf4372ee13c8441c","tid":940353,"uid":1982,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"香港特區警察仲耐過中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b19ed12020d82f734b2b7a01d53361035aad1330","tid":940353,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"由英國開始創立香港警隊果陣計咪175年"},{"pid":"ac154c9e3b3a6803c621e977c38b67a3ccd1c417","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:05:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://castnet.nctu.edu.tw/files/images_db/143/20120422031811.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcastnet.nctu.edu.tw%2Ffiles%2Fimages_db%2F143%2F20120422031811.jpg&h=90fee674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://attach.bbs.miui.com/forum/201111/11/021522tuhylwytyykfdthq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fattach.bbs.miui.com%2Fforum%2F201111%2F11%2F021522tuhylwytyykfdthq.jpg&h=ba991fc7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b7d6993a141fd1365d261a2d6bb70a38a81deca","tid":940353,"uid":191926,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:06:01.000Z","msg":"香港警察成立175年<br />\n黨衛警察成立22年<br />\n香港警察滅亡22年"},{"pid":"542ee99d69e03577fe20dc38ad9000475bd737a8","tid":940353,"uid":24104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:06:21.000Z","msg":"有乜撚嘢人會炒你啲入場卷呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7d6647518ba6382c6de46fd440aa890b495a7e","tid":940353,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:07:26.000Z","msg":"記得唔知香港駐邊度嘅代表處慶祝成立50年<br />\n點知梁振英話香港只係回歸咗20年<br />\n所以唔應該慶祝"},{"pid":"b8174fdd56931cae724a6ddad8add7a5c0eb0b18","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/isHpGh68eWGr2pxLgFgOlw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTYwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--/https://s.yimg.com/ob/image/74856d03-e0ac-40fc-ac92-77fbedf020aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FisHpGh68eWGr2pxLgFgOlw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTYwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fob%2Fimage%2F74856d03-e0ac-40fc-ac92-77fbedf020aa.jpg&h=04c782e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港皇家警隊"},{"pid":"42bccfe0dedd9b2cc0c7addfe52939b2f2bd82ba","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b8174fdd56931cae724a6ddad8add7a5c0eb0b18","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/xd/api/res/1.2/isHpGh68eWGr2pxLgFgOlw--/YXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTYwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--/https://s.yimg.com/ob/image/74856d03-e0ac-40fc-ac92-77fbedf020aa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fxd%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FisHpGh68eWGr2pxLgFgOlw--%2FYXBwaWQ9eXR3YXVjdGlvbnNlcnZpY2U7aD00NTA7cT04NTtyb3RhdGU9YXV0bzt3PTYwMDtwPW9wZW5jdg--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fob%2Fimage%2F74856d03-e0ac-40fc-ac92-77fbedf020aa.jpg&h=04c782e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港皇家警隊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:14:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.mingpaocanada.com/TOR/ftp/News/20180906/HK/_06go402.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2FTOR%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20180906%2FHK%2F_06go402.jpg&h=508a9e2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港特區警察升旗"},{"pid":"82e5830b18116d2bb8760b1184d2852b99f90e97","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b19ed12020d82f734b2b7a01d53361035aad1330","tid":940353,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"由英國開始創立香港警隊果陣計咪175年"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"香港皇家警隊已於97年6月30日解散"},{"pid":"029fc251cde51504c890e17df0018023e55ffff5","tid":940353,"uid":17641,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:18:33.000Z","msg":"又係到叨英國人光，而家係特區公安，成立21年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4117708fc43564386290fe45c640bf7e5b6c54e","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:22:51.000Z","msg":"1980年代香港皇家警隊誓詞<br />\n閣下（ 姓名 ）於（日期）宣誓就職，以警務人員身份，<span style=\"color: red;\">願依法竭誠效忠英女皇陛下伊麗莎白二世，其儲君及繼任人，並願遵守香港法律</span>，維護法綱，執行法紀，勵行職守，秉公行事，不枉不徇，並絕對服從上級一切合法命令。<br />\n<br />\n97年後香港特區警察誓詞<br />\n本人..................... *謹向全能之主發誓 / 謹以至誠作出宣言 ｝ <span style=\"color: red;\">本人會竭誠依法為香港特別行政區政府效力為 警務人員，遵從支持及維護香港特別行政區的法律</span>，以不畏懼、不徇私、不對他人懷惡意、不敵視他人及忠誠努力的態度行使職權，執行職務，並且毫不懷疑地服從上級長官的一切合法命令。"},{"pid":"25da29827d1ab9631218af0b6b2a4851531d7099","tid":940353,"uid":63181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"皇家頭銜唔係應該放最前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e3e3f326ca916b8d9541f2075c03d5c9d88a245","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25da29827d1ab9631218af0b6b2a4851531d7099","tid":940353,"uid":63181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:26:27.000Z","msg":"皇家頭銜唔係應該放最前 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:31:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n應該係：<br />\nRoyal Hong Kong Police<br />\n皇家香港警察(隊)"},{"pid":"b83b1dc3a54626a56696181a28c15c9057e3662a","tid":940353,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b19ed12020d82f734b2b7a01d53361035aad1330","tid":940353,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"由英國開始創立香港警隊果陣計咪175年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"咁計同亞視計埋麗的然後話自己係香港歷史最悠久電視台有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07ce52d5f68467b757c2964be6ac45cbe7d96377","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b83b1dc3a54626a56696181a28c15c9057e3662a","tid":940353,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b19ed12020d82f734b2b7a01d53361035aad1330","tid":940353,"uid":107927,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:05:09.000Z","msg":"由英國開始創立香港警隊果陣計咪175年"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:40:03.000Z","msg":"咁計同亞視計埋麗的然後話自己係香港歷史最悠久電視台有乜分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:55:57.000Z","msg":"由麗的有線電視計起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc01238a4c5434b3df300757bea59f64c252eb18","tid":940353,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de67e8851f7977a42fb9808cdf4372ee13c8441c","tid":940353,"uid":1982,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T01:04:38.000Z","msg":"香港特區警察